CNCP v1 23388
{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#9591: Attribute Inheritance broken when comment in template root",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:23:29.272182+00:00",
  "text": "Attribute Inheritance broken when comment in template root\n\n### Vue version\n\n3.3.8\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://play.vuejs.org/#\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nCreate a Component with a comment in template root\r\n\r\n```vue\r\n<template>\r\n<!-- comment -->\r\n<div>\r\n  Title\r\n</div>\r\n</template>\r\n```\r\nUse the component.\r\n\r\n```vue\r\n<script setup>\r\nimport { ref } from 'vue'\r\nimport Comp from './Comp.vue';\r\n\r\nconst msg = ref('Hello World!')\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<template>\r\n  <h1>{{ msg }}</h1>\r\n  <input v-model=\"msg\">\r\n  <Comp style=\"color: blue;\" />\r\n</template>\r\n```\n\n### What is expected?\n\n![image](https://github.com/vuejs/core/assets/84779491/a566da53-c158-4845-b547-f2e439ce7210)\r\n\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\n![image](https://github.com/vuejs/core/assets/84779491/d081b41e-b3a4-4144-8c67-b4903b6a2ac9)\r\n\n\n### System Info\n\n_No response_\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n_No response_",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    "scope: playground"
  ],
